<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<script src="../codemirror/lib/codemirror.js"></script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../codemirror/lib/codemirror.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../codemirror/theme/material.css">
</head>
<body>
<textarea class="codemirror-textarea" id="codemirror" nodeintegration>
{
  "path": "./Files",
  "name": "Files",
  "type": "folder",
  "children": [
    {
      "path": "./Files/folderOpen.json",
      "name": "folderOpen.json",
      "type": "file",
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "path": "./Files/folderOpen.json.html",
      "name": "folderOpen.json.html",
      "type": "file",
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "path": "./Files/folderOpen.json.html.html",
      "name": "folderOpen.json.html.html",
      "type": "file",
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "path": "./Files/folderOpen.json.html.json",
      "name": "folderOpen.json.html.json",
      "type": "file",
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "path": "./Files/folderOpen.json.json",
      "name": "folderOpen.json.json",
      "type": "file",
      "children": []
    }
  ]
}
</textarea>
<script type="text/javascript">
var textArea = document.getElementById('codemirror');
var editor = CodeMirror.fromTextArea(textArea, {
lineNumbers: true,
mode: "xml",
 htmlMode: true,
theme: "material",
});
</script>
 <script src="../JS/require.js"></script>
<script src="../JS/requires.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
